snippet.title: Wood & Weather - Coming 2050 (or sooner than you think)
snippet.description:
Wood & Weather is a single player god-game set in a wooden toy city. https://store.steampowered.com/app/1677010/Wood__Weather/
Make friends and control the weather as an ethereal blue hand in a surprising little open world. 🌤 🌦 ⛈ ❄️ ☂️ 🍃 Coming 2050 (or sooner than you think) 

Website: https://www.woodweather.com
Paper House: https://www.paperhousegames.com

Music by Dan Golding
